diff --git a/docs/CONTROL_API.md b/docs/CONTROL_API.md
index d5f7c8c..28b3e19 100644
--- a/docs/CONTROL_API.md
+++ b/docs/CONTROL_API.md
@@ -210,3 +210,25 @@ read-only import data.
 
 `POST /control/v1/secrets:rotate` rotates the local encrypted store. Rotation is
 rejected when the master key is environment-owned.
+
+## Revision-safe management and hot reload
+
+All configuration mutations require an expected revision and an
+`Idempotency-Key`. The daemon validates a candidate before provider construction,
+publishes only a fully built runtime, persists the new revision, and restores the
+prior runtime if persistence fails.
+
+| Endpoint | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `POST /control/v1/config:validate` | Preview changed and restart-required paths |
+| `PATCH /control/v1/config` | Apply a complete desired configuration |
+| `POST /control/v1/config:rollback` | Restore last-known-good configuration |
+| `PATCH /control/v1/providers/{provider}` | Enable/disable and edit allowed models |
+| `PATCH /control/v1/providers/{provider}/accounts/{account}` | Enable, label, or reprioritize an account |
+| `DELETE /control/v1/providers/{provider}/accounts/{account}` | Remove an account and its daemon-owned secrets |
+| `PATCH /control/v1/routing` | Update default route and explicit model map |
+
+Stale writers receive `409`. Anonymous Kilo remains free-only, provider-prefixed
+routing remains isolated, and no mutation invokes systemd, Docker, a shell, or
+process self-restart. Port/listener changes are stored as desired state and
+reported as restart-required rather than applied unsafely in-process.
diff --git a/docs/qa/ya-tui-08.md b/docs/qa/ya-tui-08.md
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..433182e
--- /dev/null
+++ b/docs/qa/ya-tui-08.md
@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@
+# YA-TUI-08 acceptance evidence
+
+- Stale expected revisions fail deterministically and cannot overwrite a newer writer.
+- Validation, provider construction, runtime publication, persistence, and rollback form one bounded transaction.
+- Failed provider construction or rejected apply leaves desired/effective state and data-plane snapshot unchanged.
+- Kilo anonymous paid-model restrictions and provider-prefix isolation remain validated.
+- Port/listener changes are restart-required; no code path invokes systemd, Docker, a shell, or self-restart.
diff --git a/internal/config/types.go b/internal/config/types.go
